src:
Happy birthday Kathleen Junio

01 Nov 2019, 11:10

BELATED birthday greetings to Kathleen Junio, of Pugo, Bayambang, Pangasinan, who turned a blessed year older last October 27, 2019. May you grow lovelier everyday and be showered with happiness, devoted friends and a caring family. On your birthday, I give you my special love, care and attention. I love you. Greetings coming from Albert Cansino of Woodside, New York, USA.
